data.title: IBM Tivoli ITM Data Collection
data.meta_description: Data Manager accepts data from IBM Tivoli ITM for AIX, Linux, UNIX, and Windows. Data Manager connects to Tivoli ITM RDBMS Interface Module (RIM) databases and to Tivoli ITM data warehouse databases using Java Database Connectivity (JDBC).
